Content.title: Darren Ferguson
Content.name: Darren Ferguson
Content.bodyText:
Thanks for the details! If you have any more details on places that we haven't tried yet then please let me know.

The waitress was actually pretty prompt and normal, though I love the fact that they use the stationery from the last restaurant rather than print their own.

I work next to Fressen too which was the only reason we went there... Unfortunately the Kingsland road is just too far for a quick lunch.
